leadership is organizational,

00:07:33.250 --> 00:07:34.239
it's not personal.

00:07:34.239 --> 00:07:35.780
And the other
responsibility you have

00:07:35.780 --> 00:07:39.930
is to maximize shareholder
return revenue.

00:07:39.930 --> 00:07:41.780
