00:36:56.960 --> 00:36:59.390
the first-ever young,
effectively, young legacy

00:36:59.390 --> 00:36:59.984
makers.

00:36:59.984 --> 00:37:02.150
The ones who don't have
fully formed and established

00:37:02.150 --> 00:37:03.920
businesses, but who
are making active

00:37:03.920 --> 00:37:07.690
change to the way culture and
society work and behave today.

00:37:07.690 --> 00:37:09.000
There are five recipients.

00:37:09.000 --> 00:37:11.300
There are two young activists
who are 11 years old,

00:37:11.300 --> 00:37:13.341
who have been in the news
a fair amount recently.

00:37:13.341 --> 00:37:15.230
There are two slightly
older, but still young

00:37:15.230 --> 00:37:20.270
activists who got notoriety
on a "Forbes" list.

00:37:20.270 --> 00:37:23.300
And there's a young
interesting filmmaker,

00:37:23.300 --> 00:37:26.360
who's gotten notoriety at
the Sundance Film Festival.

00:37:26.360 --> 00:37:28.710
We're passing forward
grants to them as well.

00:37:28.710 --> 00:37:30.470
So if you're curious
to come hear more--

00:37:30.470 --> 00:37:31.820
either more about
the book, and we're

