And with that, on
behalf of Lucas and me,

00:37:41.590 --> 00:37:44.090
I just want to say thank you
for giving us some of your time

00:37:44.090 --> 00:37:45.788
today and joining us.

00:37:45.788 --> 00:37:46.913
LUCAS CONLEY: Thanks, guys.

00:37:46.913 --> 00:37:49.328
[APPLAUSE]

